<font color="yellow">I'm telling the truth.</font>

428
00:28:57,396 --> 00:28:59,096
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

429
00:29:00,556 --> 00:29:01,696
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

430
00:29:35,496 --> 00:29:37,456
<font color="yellow">Come again.</font>

