00:29:39,796 --> 00:29:41,096
<font color="yellow">Come again.</font>

432
00:29:43,056 --> 00:29:44,256
<font color="yellow">When did you come?</font>

433
00:29:44,756 --> 00:29:45,926
<font color="yellow">Just now.</font>

434
00:29:46,396 --> 00:29:48,626
<font color="yellow">Why did you come? I can handle it alone.</font>

435
00:29:48,956 --> 00:29:51,126
<font color="yellow">You can go home and rest. You can watch the kids.</font>

436
00:29:53,496 --> 00:29:55,296
<font color="yellow">I don't have any kids to watch.</font>

437
00:29:55,696 --> 00:29:56,696
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

438
00:29:56,996 --> 00:29:59,156
<font color="yellow">I lost all my kids.</font>

439
00:29:59,426 --> 00:30:00,626
<font color="yellow">To whom?</font>

440
00:30:00,726 --> 00:30:02,256
<font color="yellow">Who do you think?</font>

441
00:30:03,856 --> 00:30:05,926
<font color="yellow">I'm telling you for the last time.</font>

442
00:30:06,496 --> 00:30:10,496
<font color="yellow">I decided not to care about our biological relation.</font>

443
00:30:11,056 --> 00:30:13,196
<font color="yellow">Once a son, always a son.</font>

444
00:30:13,596 --> 00:30:14,596
<font color="yellow">Got it?</font>

445
00:30:14,856 --> 00:30:16,256
<font color="yellow">Remember that.</font>

446
00:30:16,426 --> 00:30:18,456
<font color="yellow">Now, stop talking about that magic nonsense...</font>

447
00:30:18,726 --> 00:30:21,296
<font color="yellow">and start studying hard again.</font>

448
00:30:21,426 --> 00:30:22,496
<font color="yellow">Do you understand?</font>

449
00:30:23,426 --> 00:30:24,656
<font color="yellow">What if I don't want to?</font>

450
00:30:24,656 --> 00:30:25,826
<font color="yellow">You still have to do it.</font>

451
00:30:25,856 --> 00:30:28,126
<font color="yellow">You will study hard again like you used to.</font>

452
00:30:28,126 --> 00:30:31,056
<font color="yellow">I will make sure that happens.</font>

453
00:30:33,396 --> 00:30:36,056
<font color="yellow">I'm going to rip all my books!</font>

454
00:30:40,126 --> 00:30:41,126
<font color="yellow">Okay. Rip them all you like.</font>

455
00:30:41,896 --> 00:30:43,896
<font color="yellow">Rip them if that will help you relieve stress.</font>

456
00:30:44,156 --> 00:30:47,226
<font color="yellow">As long as you will study hard again like you used to,</font>

457
00:30:47,296 --> 00:30:50,056
<font color="yellow">I will gladly buy more than 1,000 books.</font>

458
00:30:50,596 --> 00:30:53,256
<font color="yellow">Why don't you keep ripping them?</font>

459
00:30:53,756 --> 00:30:54,926
<font color="yellow">Keep ripping.</font>

460
00:30:55,556 --> 00:30:57,356
<font color="yellow">I will come back in exactly 10 minutes.</font>

461
00:31:09,626 --> 00:31:11,196
<font color="yellow">Ah In, are you done, Darling?</font>

462
00:31:13,826 --> 00:31:15,496
<font color="yellow">Yes. Here.</font>

463
00:31:18,356 --> 00:31:20,626
<font color="yellow">You did very well.</font>

464
00:31:20,826 --> 00:31:23,826
<font color="yellow">Ah In, you are much better than the boys.</font>

465
00:31:24,096 --> 00:31:25,226
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

466
00:31:25,796 --> 00:31:27,326
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

467
00:31:27,626 --> 00:31:30,426
<font color="yellow">Ah In, you studied 50 words.</font>

468
00:31:30,656 --> 00:31:32,396
<font color="yellow">Should we study 50 more words?</font>

469
00:31:32,596 --> 00:31:34,926
<font color="yellow">- Okay. - You can do it, right?</font>

470
00:31:35,796 --> 00:31:39,396
<font color="yellow">You have to write 50 words 10 times, so that's 500 words.</font>

471
00:31:44,626 --> 00:31:45,696
<font color="yellow">Mom.</font>

472
00:31:46,326 --> 00:31:48,256
<font color="yellow">You're home, Son.</font>

473
00:31:48,256 --> 00:31:49,296
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

474
00:31:49,426 --> 00:31:50,426
<font color="yellow">Was it not too cold outside?</font>

475
00:31:50,426 --> 00:31:51,456
<font color="yellow">It was a little cold.</font>

476
00:31:51,456 --> 00:31:53,256
<font color="yellow">Right. Ah In needs to study.</font>

477
00:31:53,326 --> 00:31:55,726
<font color="yellow">Shall we go to your room and talk?</font>

478
00:31:55,756 --> 00:31:56,956
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

479
00:31:58,296 --> 00:31:59,556
<font color="yellow">Ah In, keep going.</font>

480
00:31:59,696 --> 00:32:00,956
<font color="yellow">- Okay. - Okay.</font>

481
00:32:00,956 --> 00:32:01,996
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

482
00:32:12,096 --> 00:32:14,596
<font color="yellow">I am sorry I had to take care of Ji Hoon and Ah In...</font>

483
00:32:14,596 --> 00:32:16,026
<font color="yellow">and I couldn't go with you.</font>

484
00:32:16,226 --> 00:32:18,156
<font color="yellow">Did you give your teacher the lesson fee?</font>

485
00:32:18,356 --> 00:32:20,326
<font color="yellow">Yes. My teacher said...</font>

486
00:32:20,326 --> 00:32:22,696
<font color="yellow">only little kids come with their parents,</font>

487
00:32:22,896 --> 00:32:24,656
<font color="yellow">so I should come alone from now on.</font>

488
00:32:24,726 --> 00:32:27,156
<font color="yellow">No, I need to go...</font>

489
00:32:27,156 --> 00:32:30,756
<font color="yellow">to check how much you've progressed.</font>

490
00:32:31,096 --> 00:32:32,656
<font color="yellow">We will go together next time, okay?</font>

491
00:32:33,056 --> 00:32:35,456
<font color="yellow">RIght. How was today's lesson?</font>

492
00:32:35,656 --> 00:32:37,526
<font color="yellow">I practiced vocalization all day again.</font>

493
00:32:37,826 --> 00:32:40,156
<font color="yellow">Mom, honestly, it's too tiring and boring.</font>

494
00:32:40,326 --> 00:32:41,426
<font color="yellow">No, Chang Soo.</font>

495
00:32:41,796 --> 00:32:44,026
<font color="yellow">The strongest person is he who endures boredom.</font>

496
00:32:44,526 --> 00:32:46,926
<font color="yellow">You have to endure repeating the same things...</font>

497
00:32:47,156 --> 00:32:49,056
<font color="yellow">and practice everyday.</font>

498
00:32:49,056 --> 00:32:51,256
<font color="yellow">Only then, you can be a great vocalist.</font>

499
00:32:51,426 --> 00:32:54,226
<font color="yellow">- Okay? - Okay, Mom.</font>

500
00:32:55,196 --> 00:32:57,796
<font color="yellow">I am so proud of you, my son.</font>

501
00:32:58,356 --> 00:32:59,356
<font color="yellow">Go take a shower.</font>

502
00:32:59,896 --> 00:33:03,426
<font color="yellow">You need to get good grades to enter the art school.</font>

503
00:33:03,726 --> 00:33:05,396
<font color="yellow">Why don't you study with me?</font>

504
00:33:05,656 --> 00:33:07,156
<font color="yellow">Sure. Mom,</font>

505
00:33:07,496 --> 00:33:10,326
<font color="yellow">I feel like I'm destined to sing and study.</font>

506
00:33:11,926 --> 00:33:13,526
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

507
00:33:13,526 --> 00:33:16,256
<font color="yellow">You're such a good boy.</font>

508
00:33:16,556 --> 00:33:18,996
<font color="yellow">That's my boy.</font>

509
00:33:19,156 --> 00:33:20,996
<font color="yellow">How lovely you are.</font>

510
00:33:21,126 --> 00:33:22,956
<font color="yellow">Do you think that's what I wanted?</font>

511
00:33:23,056 --> 00:33:25,556
<font color="yellow">I tried to stop her, saying this is nonsense.</font>

512
00:33:25,596 --> 00:33:26,656
<font color="yellow">Then, what?</font>

513
00:33:26,696 --> 00:33:28,396
<font color="yellow">But Hee Sook...</font>

514
00:33:28,396 --> 00:33:31,696
<font color="yellow">lost her mind and fiercely yelled at me.</font>

515
00:33:32,556 --> 00:33:34,896
<font color="yellow">I couldn't fight with her in front of the kids, so I just left.</font>

516
00:33:35,726 --> 00:33:39,326
<font color="yellow">Gosh. She completely beat you.</font>

517
00:33:39,556 --> 00:33:41,796
<font color="yellow">She told me not to come home before midnight.</font>

518
00:33:41,856 --> 00:33:44,156
<font color="yellow">Really? You did a great job.</font>

519
00:33:44,326 --> 00:33:46,256
<font color="yellow">- And... - What is it?</font>

520
00:33:46,556 --> 00:33:48,826
<font color="yellow">she asked if you can sleep in the restaurant and not come home.</font>

521
00:33:49,826 --> 00:33:52,026
<font color="yellow">- What? - She said the kids can't...</font>

522
00:33:52,026 --> 00:33:54,956
<font color="yellow">sleep tight because of your snoring. And they can't study well next day.</font>

523
00:33:54,996 --> 00:33:56,396
<font color="yellow">So she wants you to live here.</font>

524
00:33:56,626 --> 00:33:59,356
<font color="yellow">- What? - This is unbelievable.</font>

525
00:34:01,756 --> 00:34:04,626
<font color="yellow">Honey, what should we do with her?</font>

526
00:34:05,256 --> 00:34:07,626
<font color="yellow">We can never defeat her at all.</font>

527
00:34:07,626 --> 00:34:08,996
<font color="yellow">What do we do now?</font>

528
00:34:12,256 --> 00:34:13,356
<font color="yellow">I have a headache.</font>

529
00:34:16,126 --> 00:34:18,496
<font color="yellow">Chang Soo, are you studying?</font>

530
00:34:18,956 --> 00:34:19,956
<font color="yellow">Yes, Mom.</font>

531
00:34:21,226 --> 00:34:23,356
<font color="yellow">- I love you. - Me, too.</font>

532
00:34:36,526 --> 00:34:38,196
<font color="yellow">Ji Hoon, did you tear the book apart?</font>

533
00:34:38,356 --> 00:34:41,226
<font color="yellow">I bought three more copies for you.</font>

534
00:34:54,356 --> 00:34:56,456
<font color="yellow">What happened to Ryu Myung Jin?</font>

535
00:34:56,526 --> 00:34:59,926
<font color="yellow">It's him who sang songs in your room, right?</font>

536
00:35:00,156 --> 00:35:02,196
<font color="yellow">Gosh. How did you know that?</font>

537
00:35:02,596 --> 00:35:05,596
<font color="yellow">I ran into him at the faculty cafeteria. What's going on?</font>

538
00:35:06,026 --> 00:35:07,926
<font color="yellow">Why is he in Korea now?</font>

539
00:35:08,096 --> 00:35:11,426
<font color="yellow">That's enough. He's Jeong Eun's dad.</font>

540
00:35:11,596 --> 00:35:14,596
<font color="yellow">He's not my daughter's dad. I don't know him.</font>

541
00:35:14,756 --> 00:35:18,426
<font color="yellow">He'd disappeared for 30 years. How can he be Jeong Eun's dad?</font>

542
00:35:18,566 --> 00:35:21,596
<font color="yellow">Tell me why he's here.</font>

543
00:35:50,026 --> 00:35:51,726
<font color="yellow">I will wait just three months,</font>

544
00:35:53,356 --> 00:35:54,996
<font color="yellow">and if I can't still get over him,</font>

545
00:35:56,026 --> 00:35:57,526
<font color="yellow">I'll move to New York, too.</font>

546
00:36:09,956 --> 00:36:11,156
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

547
00:36:15,396 --> 00:36:16,456
<font color="yellow">Dad!</font>

548
00:36:20,626 --> 00:36:22,156
<font color="yellow">How have you been, my daughter?</font>

549
00:36:22,926 --> 00:36:25,526
<font color="yellow">Dad!</font>

550
00:36:27,296 --> 00:36:30,826
<font color="yellow">- When did you come back? - It's been a couple of days.</font>

551
00:36:30,826 --> 00:36:32,496
<font color="yellow">Let me see...</font>

552
00:36:32,496 --> 00:36:35,156
<font color="yellow">if you've become more beautiful during the last six months.</font>

553
00:36:35,296 --> 00:36:38,326
<font color="yellow">You've become more handsome.</font>

554
00:36:38,426 --> 00:36:39,426
<font color="yellow">Do you think so?</font>

555
00:36:40,296 --> 00:36:42,126
<font color="yellow">Dad.</font>

556
00:36:42,256 --> 00:36:44,456
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

557
00:36:46,326 --> 00:36:50,726
<font color="yellow">This is espresso, your favorite.</font>

558
00:36:50,856 --> 00:36:53,596
<font color="yellow">Please try it. It is as good as the ones you had in Italy.</font>

559
00:37:03,426 --> 00:37:04,426
<font color="yellow">It's great.</font>

560
00:37:09,156 --> 00:37:12,226
<font color="yellow">Anyway, why did you return to Korea?</font>

561
00:37:12,626 --> 00:37:15,226
<font color="yellow">You didn't tell me you'd come back.</font>

562
00:37:16,326 --> 00:37:18,026
<font color="yellow">You appeared...</font>

563
00:37:18,796 --> 00:37:21,396
<font color="yellow">in my life one day out of the blue.</font>

564
00:37:23,796 --> 00:37:26,226
<font color="yellow">Is it because I visited you when I was traveling?</font>

565
00:37:26,356 --> 00:37:27,726
<font color="yellow">That's right.</font>

566
00:37:28,026 --> 00:37:30,996
<font color="yellow">I needed some time to cancel the operas...</font>

567
00:37:31,726 --> 00:37:35,296
<font color="yellow">scheduled to be held in Italy and France. That's why I came late.</font>

568
00:37:37,066 --> 00:37:38,426
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

569
00:37:41,726 --> 00:37:42,956
<font color="yellow">Have you...</font>

570
00:37:43,626 --> 00:37:46,096
<font color="yellow">met with Mom?</font>

571
00:37:46,726 --> 00:37:47,726
<font color="yellow">I have.</font>

572
00:37:48,696 --> 00:37:51,196
<font color="yellow">What did she say?</font>

573
00:37:51,496 --> 00:37:53,596
<font color="yellow">Didn't she hurt you or something?</font>

574
00:37:53,826 --> 00:37:55,726
<font color="yellow">I'm sure she didn't just let you go.</font>

575
00:37:56,566 --> 00:37:58,526
<font color="yellow">She dashed away.</font>

576
00:37:59,826 --> 00:38:03,326
<font color="yellow">You should've talked to me first before you went to see her.</font>

577
00:38:03,396 --> 00:38:06,926
<font color="yellow">You shouldn't have met her alone that recklessly.</font>

578
00:38:06,926 --> 00:38:09,066
<font color="yellow">Dad, you are in danger.</font>

579
00:38:09,156 --> 00:38:11,826
<font color="yellow">You really are in danger.</font>

580
00:38:12,856 --> 00:38:15,426
<font color="yellow">I know. It's been about 30 years.</font>

581
00:38:17,356 --> 00:38:20,326
<font color="yellow">- Dad... - Right, Jeong Eun.</font>

582
00:38:20,826 --> 00:38:23,326
<font color="yellow">- Why don't you come to my concert? - Sorry?</font>

583
00:38:24,126 --> 00:38:25,356
<font color="yellow">Come with your mom.</font>

584
00:38:34,196 --> 00:38:35,396
<font color="yellow">(World-renowned Baritone Ryu Myung Jin, Comeback concert)</font>

585
00:38:37,956 --> 00:38:41,426
<font color="yellow">Dad, I can be there, but...</font>

586
00:38:41,896 --> 00:38:44,496
<font color="yellow">You must bring your mom, too.</font>

587
00:38:48,826 --> 00:38:49,856
<font color="yellow">Dad,</font>

588
00:38:50,656 --> 00:38:52,826
<font color="yellow">she might set off a bomb...</font>

589
00:38:53,596 --> 00:38:57,196
<font color="yellow">at the concert hall. Then, it will ruin your concert.</font>

590
00:39:01,156 --> 00:39:02,456
<font color="yellow">That's what I want.</font>

591
00:39:03,856 --> 00:39:07,326
<font color="yellow">- Pardon? - I loved Ae Ri with all my heart...</font>

592
00:39:07,526 --> 00:39:09,956
<font color="yellow">in my vigorous youth. If it's her who detonates a bomb,</font>

593
00:39:10,296 --> 00:39:11,656
<font color="yellow">I am more than willing...</font>

594
00:39:12,926 --> 00:39:13,926
<font color="yellow">to die.</font>

595
00:39:14,496 --> 00:39:17,096
<font color="yellow">Dying on the stage while singing...</font>

596
00:39:17,356 --> 00:39:19,426
<font color="yellow">by the lady I love...</font>

597
00:39:19,596 --> 00:39:21,156
<font color="yellow">is so dramatic, isn't it?</font>

598
00:39:21,756 --> 00:39:24,856
<font color="yellow">That's what my lifetime dream is.</font>

599
00:39:27,626 --> 00:39:28,926
<font color="yellow">Dad...</font>

600
00:39:30,356 --> 00:39:33,626
<font color="yellow">Espresso has an aroma of men.</font>

601
00:39:34,066 --> 00:39:36,826
<font color="yellow">What? She didn't give you the money back?</font>

602
00:39:37,156 --> 00:39:39,826
<font color="yellow">No, Mother. I can't tell her to pay back...</font>

603
00:39:39,826 --> 00:39:41,756
<font color="yellow">since I'm her mother-in-law.</font>

604
00:39:41,856 --> 00:39:42,896
<font color="yellow">How much is it?</font>

605
00:39:43,496 --> 00:39:45,296
<font color="yellow">It's 79 dollars.</font>

606
00:39:46,156 --> 00:39:50,126
<font color="yellow">That's too little. Just think you paid for her this time.</font>

607
00:39:50,496 --> 00:39:54,226
<font color="yellow">Mother, it's a lot to me.</font>

608
00:39:54,226 --> 00:39:56,756
<font color="yellow">I don't get pension, and my sons do not pay rent.</font>

609
00:39:56,756 --> 00:39:59,426
<font color="yellow">I barely make my both ends meet with the money I saved...</font>

610
00:39:59,426 --> 00:40:01,126
<font color="yellow">with the pension.</font>

611
00:40:01,256 --> 00:40:05,256
<font color="yellow">So 79 dollars is a large amount of money to me.</font>

612
00:40:05,456 --> 00:40:09,126
<font color="yellow">That's the amount we can live a week on.</font>

613
00:40:09,656 --> 00:40:11,196
<font color="yellow">Do you think she has no plan to pay back?</font>

614
00:40:11,326 --> 00:40:14,726
<font color="yellow">Yes. I went to her place for that money,</font>

615
00:40:15,396 --> 00:40:17,066
<font color="yellow">but she just said,</font>

616
00:40:17,066 --> 00:40:19,496
<font color="yellow">"What brings you here, Mother", blinking her eyes like this.</font>

617
00:40:19,496 --> 00:40:23,256
<font color="yellow">I couldn't tell her to give me the money, so I just left.</font>

618
00:40:24,026 --> 00:40:25,296
<font color="yellow">- Dear me. - What should I do?</font>

619
00:40:28,596 --> 00:40:30,566
<font color="yellow">I'm really on a tight budget.</font>

620
00:40:31,096 --> 00:40:33,726
<font color="yellow">It's not embarrassing for children...</font>

621
00:40:33,726 --> 00:40:36,296
<font color="yellow">to ask their parents for help, while parents cannot even ask...</font>

622
00:40:36,296 --> 00:40:38,796
<font color="yellow">their kids to pay back the borrowed money.</font>

623
00:40:38,796 --> 00:40:41,426
<font color="yellow">It is so unfair.</font>

624
00:40:42,696 --> 00:40:44,326
<font color="yellow">You're right.</font>

625
00:40:45,626 --> 00:40:48,496
<font color="yellow">What should we do to make her pay it back?</font>

626
00:41:00,696 --> 00:41:02,566
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

627
00:41:03,196 --> 00:41:04,956
<font color="yellow">Don't talk to me. I'm counting money.</font>

628
00:41:06,496 --> 00:41:07,596
<font color="yellow">Actually,</font>

629
00:41:12,356 --> 00:41:15,296
<font color="yellow">I have something to tell you.</font>

630
00:41:16,066 --> 00:41:17,096
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

631
00:41:20,426 --> 00:41:23,226
<font color="yellow">What? What did you say?</font>

632
00:41:23,496 --> 00:41:24,626
<font color="yellow">Why...</font>

633
00:41:25,026 --> 00:41:27,756
<font color="yellow">are you yelling at me?</font>

634
00:41:27,896 --> 00:41:29,426
<font color="yellow">You just made me yell at you.</font>

635
00:41:29,696 --> 00:41:31,856
<font color="yellow">We don't have that large amount of money.</font>

636
00:41:31,856 --> 00:41:33,126
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

637
00:41:33,226 --> 00:41:35,456
<font color="yellow">We got the deposit back from our house in Daechi-dong.</font>

638
00:41:35,566 --> 00:41:37,426
<font color="yellow">We already spent one-third of it.</font>

639
00:41:37,426 --> 00:41:40,596
<font color="yellow">What? Where did you spend that much money on?</font>

640
00:41:40,596 --> 00:41:43,656
<font color="yellow">You haven't made money for a while, have you?</font>

