652
00:42:19,226 --> 00:42:20,256
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

653
00:42:20,756 --> 00:42:23,426
<font color="yellow">He needs to take a piano lesson...</font>

654
00:42:23,426 --> 00:42:25,426
