00:42:30,026 --> 00:42:31,126
<font color="yellow">Goodness.</font>

657
00:42:31,996 --> 00:42:35,126
<font color="yellow">Things have become terrible since they were switched.</font>

658
00:42:35,956 --> 00:42:38,496
<font color="yellow">Don't say that ever. I will make Chang Soo...</font>

659
00:42:38,796 --> 00:42:41,756
<font color="yellow">a world-class singer by any means.</font>

660
00:42:59,956 --> 00:43:01,026
<font color="yellow">What about me?</font>

661
00:43:01,096 --> 00:43:04,156
<font color="yellow">I join Minjeong Party today. I have to make a donation,</font>

662
00:43:04,156 --> 00:43:07,196
<font color="yellow">and I have to pay 20,000 dollars for the by-election.</font>

663
00:43:07,196 --> 00:43:08,656
<font color="yellow">What am I supposed to do?</font>

664
00:43:08,656 --> 00:43:10,896
<font color="yellow">Stop with the politic nonsense.</font>

665
00:43:10,896 --> 00:43:11,996
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

666
00:43:12,026 --> 00:43:14,656
<font color="yellow">Just work hard as a lawyer,</font>

667
00:43:14,656 --> 00:43:16,256
<font color="yellow">and make money. Okay?</font>

668
00:43:17,296 --> 00:43:18,826
<font color="yellow">What... What did you say?</font>

669
00:43:19,326 --> 00:43:22,296
<font color="yellow">Give me money, too. Give me money!</font>

670
00:43:22,296 --> 00:43:24,956
<font color="yellow">- Let it go. - You tore it. Give it to me.</font>

671
00:43:24,956 --> 00:43:27,496
<font color="yellow">- You're tearing them. - Let it go!</font>

672
00:43:27,596 --> 00:43:29,196
<font color="yellow">Ouch. My goodness.</font>

673
00:43:30,096 --> 00:43:33,126
<font color="yellow">- Oh, dear. My back hurts. - Gosh, my money.</font>

674
00:43:33,356 --> 00:43:34,356
<font color="yellow">My back hurts.</font>

675
00:43:34,856 --> 00:43:37,256
<font color="yellow">Grandmother, I'm here. Where are you?</font>

676
00:43:37,256 --> 00:43:39,426
<font color="yellow">We're in here. Come inside.</font>

677
00:43:41,726 --> 00:43:42,956
<font color="yellow">Grandmother. Did you want to see me?</font>

678
00:43:42,956 --> 00:43:44,956
<font color="yellow">- Come on in. - You're here, too, Mother.</font>

679
00:43:46,696 --> 00:43:48,556
<font color="yellow">Oh, my. What are you doing?</font>

680
00:43:49,056 --> 00:43:51,096
<font color="yellow">Let's play cards.</font>

681
00:43:51,456 --> 00:43:53,026
<font color="yellow">- Cards? - Yes.</font>

682
00:43:54,656 --> 00:43:56,996
<font color="yellow">Jeong Ae and I wanted to play,</font>

683
00:43:56,996 --> 00:43:59,626
<font color="yellow">but we were short one person. So I called you.</font>

684
00:44:02,526 --> 00:44:04,356
<font color="yellow">Oh... I see.</font>

685
00:44:05,856 --> 00:44:08,526
<font color="yellow">You brought some money with you, right?</font>

686
00:44:08,796 --> 00:44:10,496
<font color="yellow">No, I didn't.</font>

687
00:44:14,826 --> 00:44:17,056
<font color="yellow">Let's just start playing,</font>

688
00:44:17,626 --> 00:44:20,726
<font color="yellow">and if you lose,</font>

689
00:44:20,796 --> 00:44:23,456
<font color="yellow">go downstairs and get money. Okay?</font>

690
00:44:24,326 --> 00:44:27,396
<font color="yellow">If I lose, of course I will do that.</font>

691
00:44:27,996 --> 00:44:31,426
<font color="yellow">By the way, how much is the stake money?</font>

692
00:44:34,226 --> 00:44:35,356
<font color="yellow">Let me do it.</font>

693
00:44:38,696 --> 00:44:40,256
<font color="yellow">Here. Grab some.</font>

694
00:44:47,496 --> 00:44:49,656
<font color="yellow">I'll take one of the Bright cards.</font>

695
00:44:49,656 --> 00:44:52,556
<font color="yellow">There we go. I'm so lucky.</font>

696
00:44:52,726 --> 00:44:54,726
<font color="yellow">- I have nothing to take. - Discard one, then.</font>

697
00:44:54,956 --> 00:44:56,426
<font color="yellow">Oh, I have this.</font>

698
00:45:01,226 --> 00:45:03,796
<font color="yellow">Grandmother, you're unlucky with your second cards.</font>

699
00:45:05,356 --> 00:45:06,496
<font color="yellow">I've got three Red Ribbon cards.</font>

700
00:45:07,196 --> 00:45:09,326
<font color="yellow">Now, this will get me...</font>

701
00:45:09,896 --> 00:45:13,596
<font color="yellow">3 Red Ribbon cards and 3 Blue Ribbon cards.</font>

702
00:45:13,656 --> 00:45:16,596
<font color="yellow">Shall we continue? I call the second go.</font>

703
00:45:17,426 --> 00:45:18,656
<font color="yellow">- Oh, dear. - Goodness.</font>

704
00:45:19,356 --> 00:45:21,856
<font color="yellow">I have nothing to take. Where did they all go?</font>

705
00:45:23,196 --> 00:45:24,926
<font color="yellow">- There. - Oh, gosh.</font>

706
00:45:25,756 --> 00:45:26,796
<font color="yellow">I call the third go.</font>

707
00:45:26,796 --> 00:45:29,796
<font color="yellow">Why can't you take any cards, Mother? Look at this.</font>

708
00:45:30,826 --> 00:45:33,056
<font color="yellow">Now, Grandmother owes me nine dollars,</font>

709
00:45:33,056 --> 00:45:34,656
<font color="yellow">and Mother owes me five dollars.</font>

710
00:45:34,756 --> 00:45:36,556
<font color="yellow">My gosh. If you keep this up,</font>

711
00:45:36,556 --> 00:45:38,396
<font color="yellow">I'll have to sell my land. Here.</font>

712
00:45:38,396 --> 00:45:39,656
<font color="yellow">I don't have five dollars.</font>

713
00:45:39,826 --> 00:45:41,626
<font color="yellow">This is all I've got left.</font>

714
00:45:41,626 --> 00:45:42,756
<font color="yellow">How much is that?</font>

715
00:45:43,196 --> 00:45:44,956
<font color="yellow">It's 4 dollars and 30 cents.</font>

716
00:45:44,956 --> 00:45:46,026
<font color="yellow">Oh, my.</font>

717
00:45:46,096 --> 00:45:47,656
<font color="yellow">- Look at her. - Now,</font>

718
00:45:47,756 --> 00:45:49,996
<font color="yellow">this is our final game.</font>

719
00:45:50,956 --> 00:45:52,056
<font color="yellow">Here we go.</font>

720
00:45:53,396 --> 00:45:56,356
<font color="yellow">My goodness. I didn't know she was so good at this.</font>

721
00:45:57,526 --> 00:45:59,626
<font color="yellow">Don't cry. Why are you crying?</font>

722
00:45:59,626 --> 00:46:01,156
<font color="yellow">I don't believe you.</font>

723
00:46:01,156 --> 00:46:04,596
<font color="yellow">You said you will help me win 79 dollars from Hee Sook.</font>

724
00:46:04,596 --> 00:46:07,896
<font color="yellow">I've lost 15 dollars, let alone winning any money.</font>

725
00:46:08,126 --> 00:46:10,856
<font color="yellow">I didn't know she was so good at playing cards.</font>

726
00:46:11,756 --> 00:46:14,696
<font color="yellow">She won all our money. How can she leave...</font>

727
00:46:14,696 --> 00:46:16,626
<font color="yellow">without giving us some winner's tip?</font>

728
00:46:17,726 --> 00:46:19,696
<font color="yellow">What do I do now, Mother?</font>

729
00:46:19,856 --> 00:46:23,396
<font color="yellow">Hee Sook didn't pay me for the groceries, and I lost money to her.</font>

730
00:46:23,526 --> 00:46:25,096
<font color="yellow">You should pay me that money yourself.</font>

731
00:46:25,956 --> 00:46:27,956
<font color="yellow">Fine. I'll pay you.</font>

732
00:46:28,756 --> 00:46:30,256
<font color="yellow">Stop crying!</font>

733
00:46:33,096 --> 00:46:35,826
<font color="yellow">Is Dong Hui absent again today?</font>

734
00:46:35,926 --> 00:46:37,096
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

735
00:46:37,356 --> 00:46:39,426
<font color="yellow">Gosh, I can't believe her.</font>

736
00:46:39,526 --> 00:46:41,256
<font color="yellow">If she doesn't want to become a writer,</font>

737
00:46:41,256 --> 00:46:43,496
<font color="yellow">she should keep working hard as an office assistant.</font>

738
00:46:43,556 --> 00:46:45,726
<font color="yellow">Look at our office now with her gone.</font>

739
00:46:45,726 --> 00:46:48,426
<font color="yellow">Our office is a big mess.</font>

740
00:46:48,456 --> 00:46:50,756
<font color="yellow">Producer Kim. What are you going to do?</font>

741
00:46:51,696 --> 00:46:53,526
<font color="yellow">Leave her be. Let her quit.</font>

742
00:46:53,526 --> 00:46:56,656
<font color="yellow">- What? - She's so ungrateful.</font>

743
00:46:57,096 --> 00:46:59,826
<font color="yellow">So many people want to become a writer,</font>

744
00:46:59,826 --> 00:47:02,456
<font color="yellow">but she refuses to become one when the director loves her script...</font>

745
00:47:02,456 --> 00:47:03,526
<font color="yellow">and our company is backing her up.</font>

746
00:47:04,156 --> 00:47:07,256
<font color="yellow">Leave her be. Let her work as an office assistant forever.</font>

747
00:47:07,256 --> 00:47:09,026
<font color="yellow">Aren't you being too harsh?</font>

748
00:47:09,226 --> 00:47:11,456
<font color="yellow">Maybe Dong Hui is just afraid.</font>

749
00:47:11,656 --> 00:47:14,626
<font color="yellow">There's nothing to be afraid of. She's just acting to be weak.</font>

750
00:47:17,326 --> 00:47:19,856
<font color="yellow">Is Dong Hui absent today as well?</font>

751
00:47:19,896 --> 00:47:21,096
<font color="yellow">Yes, Ma'am.</font>

752
00:47:21,426 --> 00:47:25,156
<font color="yellow">She must be very sick. She says she can't move at all.</font>

753
00:47:25,256 --> 00:47:28,726
<font color="yellow">You don't have to cover for her. I saw her and she was fine.</font>

754
00:47:28,956 --> 00:47:29,956
<font color="yellow">Pardon?</font>

755
00:47:38,456 --> 00:47:40,426
<font color="yellow">I guess Dong Hui didn't say anything to you.</font>

756
00:47:41,096 --> 00:47:42,256
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

757
00:47:42,596 --> 00:47:44,756
<font color="yellow">I thought you would rush into my office...</font>

758
00:47:44,756 --> 00:47:46,796
<font color="yellow">and lash out at me again.</font>

759
00:47:47,256 --> 00:47:49,956
<font color="yellow">I went to see Dong Hui yesterday and asked her to sell her synopsis.</font>

760
00:47:50,026 --> 00:47:51,026
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

761
00:47:51,026 --> 00:47:52,096
<font color="yellow">What else could I do?</font>

762
00:47:52,196 --> 00:47:55,156
<font color="yellow">We already got investments, and the TV station wants her synopsis.</font>

763
00:47:55,196 --> 00:47:57,996
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui is a rookie. I didn't have any other choices.</font>

764
00:47:58,196 --> 00:48:00,356
<font color="yellow">Did you really do that?</font>

765
00:48:00,356 --> 00:48:02,256
<font color="yellow">That's why I offered her a handsome amount.</font>

766
00:48:02,826 --> 00:48:05,726
<font color="yellow">I haven't even offered that kind of money to any experienced writers.</font>

767
00:48:05,826 --> 00:48:07,356
<font color="yellow">That's not what I was asking.</font>

768
00:48:07,356 --> 00:48:08,896
<font color="yellow">Does it have to be Dong Hui?</font>

769
00:48:09,096 --> 00:48:11,096
<font color="yellow">Can't you just give her up?</font>

770
00:48:11,196 --> 00:48:14,196
<font color="yellow">This is work. I'm not doing this to take her side.</font>

771
00:48:14,556 --> 00:48:16,156
<font color="yellow">Our team's existence depends on this.</font>

772
00:48:16,156 --> 00:48:18,756
<font color="yellow">That's why you should convince her to sell her synopsis.</font>

773
00:48:19,556 --> 00:48:22,096
<font color="yellow">Tell her to decide whether she will make a waste,</font>

774
00:48:22,396 --> 00:48:24,696
<font color="yellow">or make use of it and gain a foothold.</font>

775
00:48:24,796 --> 00:48:26,656
<font color="yellow">It's not a bad offer for her.</font>

776
00:48:26,826 --> 00:48:27,996
<font color="yellow">Mi Joo.</font>

777
00:48:28,456 --> 00:48:30,696
<font color="yellow">It's been a while since you called me by my name.</font>

778
00:48:31,726 --> 00:48:33,056
<font color="yellow">We don't have much time.</font>

779
00:48:33,256 --> 00:48:35,826
<font color="yellow">The broadcasting station is rushing us to set up a meeting.</font>

780
00:48:36,926 --> 00:48:38,956
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon. Please convince her.</font>

781
00:49:05,026 --> 00:49:08,096
<font color="yellow">How can you draw red lines on my script, and leave comments like...</font>

782
00:49:08,096 --> 00:49:11,756
<font color="yellow">"It's childish", "It's cliche", "Fix it", and "I don't get this"?</font>

783
00:49:11,896 --> 00:49:13,626
<font color="yellow">How can you be so mean?</font>

784
00:49:13,626 --> 00:49:15,196
<font color="yellow">I was trying to support you.</font>

785
00:49:15,196 --> 00:49:17,496
<font color="yellow">Romantic comedy is the most sophisticated genre.</font>

786
00:49:17,496 --> 00:49:20,896
<font color="yellow">The new trend is that the drama either has a fantasy...</font>

787
00:49:20,896 --> 00:49:23,956
<font color="yellow">or fully reflects the reality.</font>

788
00:49:23,956 --> 00:49:25,096
<font color="yellow">Give it to me.</font>

789
00:49:25,096 --> 00:49:26,126
<font color="yellow">Don't move.</font>

790
00:49:26,756 --> 00:49:29,626
<font color="yellow">This is what I'm talking about. When a man and a woman meet,</font>

791
00:49:29,626 --> 00:49:31,156
<font color="yellow">they should confront each other...</font>

792
00:49:31,326 --> 00:49:33,696
<font color="yellow">without caring about reasons or courtesy.</font>

793
00:49:34,326 --> 00:49:35,856
<font color="yellow">You said you want to become a writer.</font>

794
00:49:36,656 --> 00:49:40,296
<font color="yellow">You should free yourself and be ahead of the viewers.</font>

795
00:49:41,196 --> 00:49:44,026
<font color="yellow">At this rate, the viewers won't wait for you.</font>

796
00:50:58,626 --> 00:50:59,626
<font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

797
00:51:00,356 --> 00:51:01,396
<font color="yellow">It's me.</font>

798
00:51:02,026 --> 00:51:03,826
<font color="yellow">Yes. Go ahead.</font>

799
00:51:04,226 --> 00:51:07,426
<font color="yellow">There are people who have been following me since that day.</font>

800
00:51:07,756 --> 00:51:09,726
<font color="yellow">I don't know what to do.</font>

801
00:51:09,996 --> 00:51:13,856
<font color="yellow">I can't move out, but I can't stay here, either.</font>

802
00:51:15,026 --> 00:51:18,356
<font color="yellow">Also, the company that Dong Hui works for...</font>

803
00:51:18,596 --> 00:51:20,496
<font color="yellow">is Hwashin Group.</font>

804
00:51:20,896 --> 00:51:23,426
<font color="yellow">Its name has changed, so I didn't know.</font>

805
00:51:24,226 --> 00:51:25,926
<font color="yellow">What should I do?</font>

806
00:51:26,426 --> 00:51:28,556
<font color="yellow">If something goes wrong...</font>

807
00:51:29,456 --> 00:51:31,826
<font color="yellow">I don't know what I should do.</font>

808
00:51:32,156 --> 00:51:33,296
<font color="yellow">That's bad news.</font>

809
00:51:33,926 --> 00:51:38,096
<font color="yellow">Please find Chairwoman Park as soon as possible.</font>

810
00:51:38,296 --> 00:51:41,996
<font color="yellow">Where has she been for the past 20 years?</font>

811
00:51:42,496 --> 00:51:44,196
<font color="yellow">Not once...</font>

812
00:51:44,696 --> 00:51:47,726
<font color="yellow">has she ever contacted me. How can she do that?</font>

813
00:51:48,556 --> 00:51:52,456
<font color="yellow">Is it even true that she's still alive?</font>

814
00:51:53,996 --> 00:51:55,126
<font color="yellow">How did it go?</font>

815
00:51:55,396 --> 00:51:56,396
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

816
00:51:56,526 --> 00:51:59,556
<font color="yellow">Ms. Oh Gui Boon's everyday life haven't changed much since then.</font>

817
00:52:00,496 --> 00:52:01,556
<font color="yellow">Is that so?</font>

818
00:52:01,996 --> 00:52:03,426
<font color="yellow">She didn't show...</font>

819
00:52:04,196 --> 00:52:06,726
<font color="yellow">any signs of moving out or disappearing.</font>

820
00:52:07,626 --> 00:52:09,826
<font color="yellow">She didn't meet anyone particular, either.</font>

821
00:52:10,596 --> 00:52:12,096
<font color="yellow">What kind of work...</font>

822
00:52:12,426 --> 00:52:15,026
<font color="yellow">is Dong Hui doing at my company now?</font>

823
00:52:15,296 --> 00:52:17,226
<font color="yellow">She was hired as an office assistant,</font>

824
00:52:18,026 --> 00:52:20,426
<font color="yellow">but her synopsis recently got...</font>

825
00:52:20,426 --> 00:52:22,896
<font color="yellow">an honorable mention at Channel T's contest.</font>

826
00:52:23,226 --> 00:52:26,296
<font color="yellow">She may be the writer of the new show of contents marketing team.</font>

827
00:52:28,956 --> 00:52:30,196
<font color="yellow">Writer?</font>

828
00:52:30,956 --> 00:52:31,996
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

829
00:52:37,996 --> 00:52:39,356
<font color="yellow">What's wrong, President Bang?</font>

830
00:52:41,096 --> 00:52:42,556
<font color="yellow">Nothing. I'm okay.</font>

831
00:52:43,656 --> 00:52:44,796
<font color="yellow">I just...</font>

832
00:52:46,226 --> 00:52:48,896
<font color="yellow">miss my sister-in-law who passed away.</font>

833
00:52:50,826 --> 00:52:51,926
<font color="yellow">Your sister-in-law?</font>

834
00:52:54,026 --> 00:52:55,256
<font color="yellow">My sister-in-law...</font>

835
00:52:55,726 --> 00:52:57,296
<font color="yellow">wanted to be a writer...</font>

836
00:52:58,626 --> 00:53:01,456
<font color="yellow">before she married my brother.</font>

837
00:53:04,956 --> 00:53:06,096
<font color="yellow">I...</font>

838
00:53:07,226 --> 00:53:09,056
<font color="yellow">miss her very much today.</font>

839
00:53:57,356 --> 00:53:58,656
<font color="yellow">Yes. What is it?</font>

840
00:53:59,496 --> 00:54:02,596
<font color="yellow">- Can I see you? - I'm busy, too. What is it?</font>

841
00:54:03,096 --> 00:54:04,256
<font color="yellow">I'll wait for you.</font>

842
00:54:25,726 --> 00:54:26,756
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

