00:54:31,126 --> 00:54:32,596
<font color="yellow">If you have something to say, fire it away.</font>

845
00:54:33,556 --> 00:54:37,296
<font color="yellow">You didn't come to work today, and you just stayed home.</font>

846
00:54:37,696 --> 00:54:40,326
<font color="yellow">How can you tell your boss to come to you?</font>

847
00:54:40,956 --> 00:54:42,256
<font color="yellow">Do you think of me...</font>

848
00:54:42,456 --> 00:54:45,656
<font color="yellow">- as some kind of a pushover? - I will do it.</font>

849
00:54:46,626 --> 00:54:49,556
<font color="yellow">- What? - I will give it a try.</font>

850
00:54:50,356 --> 00:54:53,126
<font color="yellow">I'll write the screenplay version of "Romance Learned through Books".</font>

851
00:54:53,556 --> 00:54:55,656
<font color="yellow">I won't sell my story to anyone.</font>

852
00:54:55,956 --> 00:54:58,626
<font color="yellow">I won't let someone else write my story.</font>

853
00:54:59,326 --> 00:55:01,956
<font color="yellow">I won't shove it in a dark corner of my room.</font>

854
00:55:02,126 --> 00:55:03,556
<font color="yellow">I will give it a try and write it.</font>

855
00:55:04,296 --> 00:55:06,296
<font color="yellow">It's my child, so I will write...</font>

856
00:55:06,326 --> 00:55:08,556
<font color="yellow">and make it see the light.</font>

857
00:55:09,726 --> 00:55:12,426
<font color="yellow">- Dong Hui. - Are you happy now?</font>

858
00:55:15,526 --> 00:55:19,096
<font color="yellow">So don't talk to me so bluntly like,</font>

859
00:55:19,156 --> 00:55:21,096
<font color="yellow">"What is it? I'm busy, too."</font>

860
00:55:23,896 --> 00:55:27,556
<font color="yellow">I'm glad you came around. Thank you, Dong Hui.</font>

861
00:55:28,056 --> 00:55:30,026
<font color="yellow">Wait.</font>

862
00:55:30,896 --> 00:55:32,056
<font color="yellow">Stay still.</font>

863
00:55:32,496 --> 00:55:35,396
<font color="yellow">Let me hug the writer who will soon become the greatest writer of Korea.</font>

864
00:55:39,126 --> 00:55:40,126
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

865
00:55:40,956 --> 00:55:43,096
<font color="yellow">honestly I am not confident about it.</font>

866
00:55:47,626 --> 00:55:50,256
<font color="yellow">Don't worry. I'm here for you.</font>

867
00:55:52,526 --> 00:55:53,526
<font color="yellow">You trust me, don't you?</font>

868
00:55:55,556 --> 00:55:56,596
<font color="yellow">I do.</font>

869
00:55:57,026 --> 00:55:59,826
<font color="yellow">We just have to keep doing what we have been doing.</font>

870
00:56:00,156 --> 00:56:02,026
<font color="yellow">We can do well.</font>

871
00:56:02,756 --> 00:56:06,326
<font color="yellow">Trust me and trust yourself.</font>

872
00:56:09,256 --> 00:56:10,256
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

873
00:56:14,456 --> 00:56:15,496
<font color="yellow">Thank you so much.</font>

874
00:56:16,496 --> 00:56:17,626
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Dong Hui.</font>

875
00:56:27,396 --> 00:56:28,396
<font color="yellow">What did you just say?</font>

876
00:56:29,226 --> 00:56:32,526
<font color="yellow">Why are you yelling?</font>

877
00:56:33,096 --> 00:56:35,756
<font color="yellow">Hey, how can I not be upset?</font>

878
00:56:35,856 --> 00:56:38,196
<font color="yellow">What did you just say? Repeat what you just said.</font>

879
00:56:38,296 --> 00:56:41,826
<font color="yellow">I did my calculation in the office.</font>

880
00:56:42,196 --> 00:56:43,696
<font color="yellow">And I realized that we've spent...</font>

881
00:56:43,696 --> 00:56:46,196
<font color="yellow">a substantial amount of money...</font>

882
00:56:46,196 --> 00:56:47,826
<font color="yellow">while raising Ji Hoon for 15 years.</font>

883
00:56:47,926 --> 00:56:50,796
<font color="yellow">The money spent on his food and clothes is okay.</font>

884
00:56:50,856 --> 00:56:51,926
<font color="yellow">But the problem is...</font>

885
00:56:52,526 --> 00:56:54,526
<font color="yellow">the money we spent on his education.</font>

886
00:56:54,526 --> 00:56:56,656
<font color="yellow">It adds up to a substantial amount, you see.</font>

887
00:56:56,656 --> 00:56:57,696
<font color="yellow">So what?</font>

888
00:56:59,256 --> 00:57:00,756
<font color="yellow">So I was thinking...</font>

889
00:57:01,796 --> 00:57:05,326
<font color="yellow">I just entered politics,</font>

890
00:57:06,496 --> 00:57:08,496
<font color="yellow">and I'm a little short on money. Can't you return...</font>

891
00:57:08,856 --> 00:57:12,156
<font color="yellow">a small portion of the money...</font>

892
00:57:12,626 --> 00:57:14,626
<font color="yellow">we have spent on Ji Hoon's education?</font>

893
00:57:14,956 --> 00:57:15,956
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

894
00:57:16,796 --> 00:57:18,756
<font color="yellow">Please?</font>

895
00:57:23,396 --> 00:57:24,796
<font color="yellow">Here you go.</font>

896
00:57:24,956 --> 00:57:27,896
<font color="yellow">- Take that and get out of here. - Hey!</font>

897
00:57:28,726 --> 00:57:31,396
<font color="yellow">No matter how desperate you are,</font>

898
00:57:31,726 --> 00:57:34,056
<font color="yellow">how can you ask to return the money you spent on your child?</font>

899
00:57:34,296 --> 00:57:36,896
<font color="yellow">We are really struggling these days!</font>

900
00:57:36,896 --> 00:57:39,896
<font color="yellow">Then you should pay for Chang Soo's vocal lessons.</font>

901
00:57:40,626 --> 00:57:42,556
<font color="yellow">Fine. We will pay for Chang Soo's education.</font>

902
00:57:42,726 --> 00:57:44,296
<font color="yellow">So send him back to us.</font>

903
00:57:46,026 --> 00:57:48,856
<font color="yellow">You said it. You're really going to pay for...</font>

904
00:57:48,856 --> 00:57:51,426
<font color="yellow">- Chang Soo's education, right? - I just said that!</font>

905
00:57:52,026 --> 00:57:54,896
<font color="yellow">- Come here. I will kill you. - Why are you...</font>

906
00:57:54,896 --> 00:57:56,956
<font color="yellow">- threatening me with a chicken? - Come here!</font>

907
00:57:57,326 --> 00:57:58,796
<font color="yellow">Come here!</font>

908
00:58:00,056 --> 00:58:02,396
<font color="yellow">- Gosh! I will get back at you! - Hey! Come here.</font>

909
00:58:02,426 --> 00:58:05,196
<font color="yellow">I am going to tell mom that you hit me.</font>

910
00:58:05,196 --> 00:58:06,826
<font color="yellow">Go ahead and tell her, you idiot!</font>

911
00:58:07,096 --> 00:58:09,426
<font color="yellow">I avoided it! How's that?</font>

912
00:58:10,196 --> 00:58:12,096
<font color="yellow">Gosh, he's unbelievable.</font>

913
00:58:16,996 --> 00:58:19,456
<font color="yellow">Goodness, I am sorry about this.</font>

914
00:58:20,256 --> 00:58:23,756
<font color="yellow">- Can I still get fried chicken? - Of course you can. Come in.</font>

915
00:58:35,356 --> 00:58:37,196
<font color="yellow">Which one would you like to order?</font>

916
00:58:38,856 --> 00:58:39,856
<font color="yellow">Actually,</font>

917
00:58:41,896 --> 00:58:43,056
<font color="yellow">I don't care about the chicken.</font>

918
00:58:45,456 --> 00:58:49,096
<font color="yellow">You are Hyung Seop's eldest son, Seong Hoon, aren't you?</font>

919
00:58:49,896 --> 00:58:50,996
<font color="yellow">Yes, I am.</font>

920
00:58:54,196 --> 00:58:57,156
<font color="yellow">- Let go of me. - You're Seong Joon, aren't you?</font>

921
00:59:07,596 --> 00:59:09,756
<font color="yellow">- Seong Hoon. - You're here.</font>

922
00:59:10,456 --> 00:59:11,696
<font color="yellow">Why did you want to see me?</font>

923
00:59:12,926 --> 00:59:14,856
<font color="yellow">I wanted to talk to you in private.</font>

924
00:59:15,226 --> 00:59:16,596
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

925
00:59:22,226 --> 00:59:24,626
<font color="yellow">What? Are you serious?</font>

926
00:59:25,396 --> 00:59:26,426
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

927
00:59:27,756 --> 00:59:29,626
<font color="yellow">What did that woman tell you?</font>

928
00:59:30,456 --> 00:59:31,926
<font color="yellow">She didn't say something else.</font>

929
00:59:32,456 --> 00:59:34,526
<font color="yellow">She mentioned Seong Joon and asked for money.</font>

930
00:59:35,496 --> 00:59:36,596
<font color="yellow">She said she wanted to open a store.</font>

931
00:59:36,996 --> 00:59:38,596
<font color="yellow">Did you give her the money or not?</font>

932
00:59:38,856 --> 00:59:42,096
<font color="yellow">Gosh, Dad. I don't have that much money on me.</font>

933
00:59:47,856 --> 00:59:48,956
<font color="yellow">Dad,</font>

934
00:59:49,726 --> 00:59:51,296
<font color="yellow">I am really sorry to ask,</font>

935
00:59:52,126 --> 00:59:53,356
<font color="yellow">but who is she?</font>

936
00:59:56,096 --> 00:59:59,096
<font color="yellow">Is she Seong Joon's biological mother?</font>

937
01:00:01,526 --> 01:00:02,726
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

938
01:00:03,356 --> 01:00:05,656
<font color="yellow">I am the handsome lawyer, Han Seong Sik.</font>

939
01:00:05,726 --> 01:00:08,826
<font color="yellow">I am the new blood of Minjeong Party, Han Seong Sik.</font>

940
01:00:08,996 --> 01:00:10,226
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

941
01:00:10,856 --> 01:00:13,826
<font color="yellow">You look like a politician now, Attorney Han.</font>

942
01:00:13,856 --> 01:00:16,156
<font color="yellow">Your infinite faith in me made everything possible.</font>

943
01:00:16,996 --> 01:00:19,726
<font color="yellow">Good luck. You should use this opportunity...</font>

944
01:00:19,856 --> 01:00:22,496
<font color="yellow">- to catch more people's attention. - I will work hard.</font>

945
01:00:24,196 --> 01:00:25,196
<font color="yellow">Attorney Han,</font>

946
01:00:26,826 --> 01:00:29,726
<font color="yellow">- congratulations. - I will remain royal forever!</font>

947
01:00:29,726 --> 01:00:31,156
<font color="yellow">- Let's do it! - Let's do it!</font>

948
01:00:31,696 --> 01:00:33,496
<font color="yellow">Let's do it!</font>

949
01:00:38,256 --> 01:00:39,256
<font color="yellow">Sir?</font>

950
01:00:43,626 --> 01:00:44,626
<font color="yellow">Sir!</font>

951
01:00:57,656 --> 01:00:58,756
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

952
01:00:59,726 --> 01:01:01,496
<font color="yellow">Why are you so surprised?</font>

953
01:01:04,326 --> 01:01:05,356
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

954
01:01:06,926 --> 01:01:08,656
<font color="yellow">Did you think I killed myself or something?</font>

955
01:01:10,496 --> 01:01:11,756
<font color="yellow">Like my father?</font>

956
01:01:17,896 --> 01:01:19,426
<font color="yellow">That's half right...</font>

957
01:01:20,796 --> 01:01:22,326
<font color="yellow">and half wrong.</font>

958
01:01:26,326 --> 01:01:28,956
<font color="yellow">I will never become like my dad.</font>

959
01:01:30,626 --> 01:01:32,426
<font color="yellow">I sat here for four days...</font>

960
01:01:33,526 --> 01:01:35,496
<font color="yellow">and tried to understand my dad.</font>

961
01:01:37,496 --> 01:01:39,296
<font color="yellow">I tried to think about how he would've felt...</font>

962
01:01:42,156 --> 01:01:43,956
<font color="yellow">and in what state he would've been in.</font>

963
01:01:51,496 --> 01:01:52,796
<font color="yellow">What should I do now?</font>

964
01:01:53,456 --> 01:01:55,096
<font color="yellow">What do you want to do?</font>

965
01:02:41,656 --> 01:02:42,726
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon.</font>

966
01:02:46,156 --> 01:02:47,726
<font color="yellow">Isn't this your phone?</font>

967
01:02:51,526 --> 01:02:54,426
<font color="yellow">It's you, Mr. Lee. Where are you coming from?</font>

968
01:02:56,996 --> 01:02:58,056
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

969
01:03:02,826 --> 01:03:04,996
<font color="yellow">President Lee. Why don't you go inside?</font>

970
01:03:09,256 --> 01:03:10,326
<font color="yellow">Goodbye.</font>

971
01:03:14,826 --> 01:03:16,526
<font color="yellow">He's a bit strange today.</font>

972
01:03:19,396 --> 01:03:21,826
<font color="yellow">What are you going to do now?</font>

973
01:03:27,656 --> 01:03:29,796
<font color="yellow">I'll do everything as I planned.</font>

974
01:03:32,996 --> 01:03:36,126
<font color="yellow">People in this town slandered my father which led to his death.</font>

975
01:03:38,156 --> 01:03:39,396
<font color="yellow">Hyung Seop's family...</font>

976
01:03:40,756 --> 01:03:42,656
<font color="yellow">made my brother die...</font>

977
01:03:42,656 --> 01:03:44,996
<font color="yellow">on the cold street in the end. I must punish them.</font>

978
01:03:47,996 --> 01:03:49,526
<font color="yellow">I'll do it as I planned.</font>

979
01:03:50,896 --> 01:03:54,226
<font color="yellow">It will greatly affect this neighborhood.</font>

980
01:03:55,656 --> 01:03:56,826
<font color="yellow">I don't care.</font>

981
01:03:57,896 --> 01:03:59,396
<font color="yellow">I'm not going to forgive them.</font>

982
01:04:01,426 --> 01:04:03,726
<font color="yellow">Inadequate forgiveness results in a tragedy.</font>

983
01:04:05,326 --> 01:04:08,656
<font color="yellow">People don't change. They can't defeat the truth.</font>

984
01:04:09,856 --> 01:04:12,796
<font color="yellow">All people are selfish.</font>

985
01:04:14,026 --> 01:04:17,756
<font color="yellow">They have to lose things they cherish and see them get destroyed.</font>

986
01:04:19,926 --> 01:04:21,326
<font color="yellow">That's when they regret their wrongdoings.</font>

987
01:04:25,226 --> 01:04:27,926
<font color="yellow">How is it going with Seong Sik?</font>

988
01:04:28,356 --> 01:04:30,456
<font color="yellow">He already joined Minjeong Party.</font>

989
01:04:30,726 --> 01:04:31,856
<font color="yellow">I think...</font>

990
01:04:32,726 --> 01:04:34,896
<font color="yellow">he will soon be nominated for the by-election.</font>

991
01:04:40,926 --> 01:04:42,356
<font color="yellow">How about Mal Ja's clinic?</font>

992
01:04:42,626 --> 01:04:44,626
<font color="yellow">It's still in operation.</font>

993
01:04:47,156 --> 01:04:48,226
<font color="yellow">Is that so?</font>

994
01:04:50,556 --> 01:04:51,696
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

995
01:05:09,856 --> 01:05:12,296
<font color="yellow">President Lee. What are you doing?</font>

996
01:05:13,356 --> 01:05:14,656
<font color="yellow">Are you okay?</font>

997
01:05:17,096 --> 01:05:18,396
<font color="yellow">I'm going to the clinic.</font>

998
01:05:21,956 --> 01:05:22,996
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

999
01:05:27,556 --> 01:05:29,426
<font color="yellow">(Yoon Surgery Clinic)</font>

1000
01:05:40,626 --> 01:05:41,796
<font color="yellow">What's wrong?</font>

1001
01:05:43,456 --> 01:05:44,796
<font color="yellow">It's nothing.</font>

1002
01:05:48,426 --> 01:05:49,856
<font color="yellow">You were fond of me.</font>

1003
01:05:50,696 --> 01:05:52,096
<font color="yellow">Why are you trembling?</font>

1004
01:05:55,256 --> 01:05:58,396
<font color="yellow">You're a doctor. I'm sure you've done this a lot.</font>

1005
01:05:59,156 --> 01:06:00,756
<font color="yellow">No. I'm not trembling.</font>

1006
01:06:02,426 --> 01:06:04,796
<font color="yellow">I just have been on edge lately.</font>

1007
01:06:08,556 --> 01:06:11,796
<font color="yellow">By the way, when did you become a doctor?</font>

1008
01:06:12,326 --> 01:06:13,426
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

1009
01:06:14,226 --> 01:06:16,256
<font color="yellow">Why are you asking?</font>

1010
01:06:16,326 --> 01:06:18,196
<font color="yellow">No reason.</font>

1011
01:06:19,156 --> 01:06:20,856
<font color="yellow">I was just curious.</font>

1012
01:06:22,626 --> 01:06:24,356
<font color="yellow">Why would you be curious about that?</font>

1013
01:06:26,456 --> 01:06:29,496
<font color="yellow">As far as I know, you were the doctor at the emergency room...</font>

1014
01:06:30,196 --> 01:06:33,726
<font color="yellow">of Seorin Hospital at the intersection 23 years ago.</font>

1015
01:06:36,526 --> 01:06:39,356
<font color="yellow">How did you know that?</font>

1016
01:06:43,326 --> 01:06:44,756
<font color="yellow">You should pick up your tweezers.</font>

1017
01:06:46,596 --> 01:06:47,596
<font color="yellow">Come on.</font>

1018
01:06:56,396 --> 01:06:57,656
<font color="yellow">You should change them.</font>

1019
01:06:58,896 --> 01:07:02,296
<font color="yellow">You're not going to use that to treat my wound, are you?</font>

1020
01:07:12,896 --> 01:07:14,126
<font color="yellow">Why did you do it?</font>

1021
01:07:15,596 --> 01:07:17,556
<font color="yellow">Do what? What?</font>

1022
01:07:21,256 --> 01:07:23,096
<font color="yellow">Your friend, Ms. Kim Geum Ja...</font>

1023
01:07:23,796 --> 01:07:26,596
<font color="yellow">ran an academy called "Geumbit Academy".</font>

1024
01:07:27,496 --> 01:07:30,096
<font color="yellow">When their bus driver had an accident while drunk driving,</font>

1025
01:07:31,626 --> 01:07:33,526
<font color="yellow">why did you fabricate the story?</font>

1026
01:07:35,496 --> 01:07:37,196
<font color="yellow">Why did you fabricate...</font>

1027
01:07:37,196 --> 01:07:39,326
<font color="yellow">the blood test result of the driver?</font>

1028
01:07:39,626 --> 01:07:40,756
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

1029
01:07:41,426 --> 01:07:42,956
<font color="yellow">I don't know about that.</font>

1030
01:07:44,856 --> 01:07:46,826
<font color="yellow">Did it break your heart...</font>

1031
01:07:47,326 --> 01:07:50,126
<font color="yellow">to see your precious children suffer a little wound?</font>

1032
01:07:52,626 --> 01:07:56,396
<font color="yellow">Is that why you thought the man who were treated as an alcoholic...</font>

1033
01:07:57,426 --> 01:08:00,296
<font color="yellow">can be treated like that forever?</font>

1034
01:08:00,296 --> 01:08:01,426
<font color="yellow">Mr. Lee.</font>

1035
01:08:02,396 --> 01:08:04,856
<font color="yellow">Who are you? Tell me who you are.</font>

1036
01:08:09,556 --> 01:08:11,726
<font color="yellow">You took your anger out on the driver,</font>

1037
01:08:12,856 --> 01:08:15,196
<font color="yellow">and that poor man hung himself.</font>

1038
01:08:16,156 --> 01:08:18,156
<font color="yellow">One of his sons...</font>

1039
01:08:19,656 --> 01:08:22,426
<font color="yellow">was hit by a dump truck and torn apart.</font>

1040
01:08:24,156 --> 01:08:25,226
<font color="yellow">Mr. Lee.</font>

1041
01:08:25,956 --> 01:08:27,056
<font color="yellow">Are you...</font>

1042
01:08:28,056 --> 01:08:30,626
<font color="yellow">the driver's son?</font>

1043
01:08:52,956 --> 01:08:54,626
<font color="yellow">(Father, I'll Take Care of You)</font>

1044
01:08:55,156 --> 01:08:57,296
<font color="yellow">Dad. Please do what she wants,</font>

1045
01:08:57,426 --> 01:09:00,196
<font color="yellow">and end things with her for Mom's sake.</font>

1046
01:09:01,596 --> 01:09:03,366
<font color="yellow">Producer Kim and Ms. Hong, please say hello.</font>

1047
01:09:03,366 --> 01:09:05,256
<font color="yellow">Hello. I'm Choi Jin Kyung.</font>

1048
01:09:05,426 --> 01:09:08,456
<font color="yellow">Is she my birth mother?</font>

1049
01:09:08,826 --> 01:09:10,826
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon. I'm here.</font>

1050
01:09:11,596 --> 01:09:15,096
<font color="yellow">Dong Hui doesn't look like her grandmother at all.</font>

1051
01:09:15,526 --> 01:09:17,366
